{
  "stem": "4513.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we were in an all-black outfit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once again, all the-- the officers and the non-commissioned officers at Fort Benjamin Harrison were white.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were telling us-- you know, things that they told us to do, just unconscionable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the fellas from Louisville, they were telling us to do-- and we said, look, we're not going to work as long as-- until we get a uniform.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not going to work in my clothes, in my-- in my suit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if the army wants me to do these kinds of things, and they want us to scrub the floors and all this sort of thing, I said, we just won't do it till we get a uniform.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said-- he mentioned that you know what can happen to you if you don't do what we tell you?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, it's not that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't think-- I'm saying to you, unless the army takes responsibility for damaging my clothes, I'm just not going to do it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, we can put you in the guardhouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, you can do anything you want to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm not going to do it, until you issue me a uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I'm in the army, then you issue me a uniform and I'll do everything you tell me to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None of us had them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None of the black soldiers at that point had them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said that they would give them to us in a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they left us alone after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they-- about two days later, we had to march through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
